data.description: This lovely home has 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and is located in Beachview Heights, the New Orleans Suburb of Kenner.  The home has 1,888 square feet of spacious living with casual and formal dining and the cozy fireplace sets the mood for entertaining. The home features all stainless-steel appliances, vinyl plank flooring, carpet in primary bedroom and plenty of storage. Spend evenings and weekends on the secluded and well-appointed patio overlooking the large back yard.  There is an impressive 12 x 20 storage building with a loft in the back yard. The convenience of the airport and I-10 and with its close proximity to Lake Front, Coconut Beach Volleyball Complex, Beachview Heights Recreational Complex, Casino and many popular restaurants makes this home an ideal choice. It is in Flood Zone X and definitely worth a showing. Property qualifies for 9,000.00 in Grant Money by local lender.
